ce of the SHMR can be used to constrain\nthe evolution of the galaxy population over cosmic time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Oct 2013 22:03:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Oct 2013 19:22:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 10 Nov 2014 20:00:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-03"}
