e the reaction and aggregation occurs to\nform the $CdS$ nanotube, thus impeding further growth of uniform CdS\nnano-tubes. Thereby we predict the necessary characteristics of reacting\nsystems which can be self assembled using suitable adaptations of previous\nexperiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Oct 2013 07:39:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-10-28"}
