ground coronal plasma plays\na key role in the CME propagation, and full MHD models should be applied when\none focusses especially on the production of a CME from a flux rope ejection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Oct 2013 15:34:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-10-28"}
